longBusinessSummary: Vidavo S.A. designs, develops, and provides connected health, wellness, and healthy ageing solutions. The company offers Vida24, a cloud based platform and customizable app that synchs multi-source data. Its platform provides chronic disease management, doctor on demand, nutrition management, e-health and wellness, marine telemedicine, behavioral change, insuretech, corporate wellbeing, wearables, scientific wellness, and digital therapeutic solutions, as well as bouquet of ehealth and mhealth modules, health assessment, and mental health. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Thessaloniki, Greece.
